00:48:44.620 --> 00:48:49.420
messenger Allah knows that they are lying and Allah bears witness that

00:48:49.420 --> 00:48:55.840
these hypocrites are liars and then Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala exposes the

00:48:55.840 --> 00:48:59.600
entire scene in the same Surah and Allah says yes he is the one who said

00:48:59.600 --> 00:49:03.360
this and he is the one who said when we go to Medina the superior will

00:49:03.360 --> 00:49:08.280
remove the inferior and he is the one who said that do not spend on these

00:49:08.280 --> 00:49:11.960
people until they leave and disperse from Muhammad salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:49:11.960 --> 00:49:16.080
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala exposes them and this is why Allah says

00:49:26.080 --> 00:49:30.400
O you who believe don't ever let your wealth and your family members

00:49:30.400 --> 00:49:35.400
distract you from the remembrance of your maker don't let that happen your

00:49:35.440 --> 00:49:39.480
family members yes we look after them your wealth yes we would like to earn

00:49:39.480 --> 00:49:44.320
but not at the expense of your faith and your belief and your religion and

00:49:44.320 --> 00:49:48.040
your link with Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala may Allah grant us sustenance that is

00:49:48.040 --> 00:49:54.920
pure and good so Usaid ibn Hudayr radiallahu anh when he heard that

00:49:54.920 --> 00:49:59.480
Abdullah ibn Ubaid ibn Salul had said the superior will remove the

00:49:59.480 --> 00:50:03.360
inferior when we get to Medina we're going to hatch a plan in order to

00:50:03.360 --> 00:50:06.800
remove Muhammad and so on he came to the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam he

00:50:06.800 --> 00:50:10.840
asked a question oh messenger why is it that we are suddenly leaving Banu

00:50:10.840 --> 00:50:14.240
al-Mustaliq we are leaving in the heat normally they would wait until it's

00:50:14.240 --> 00:50:18.160
a bit cool but they were instructed to leave in the heat the Prophet

00:50:18.160 --> 00:50:20.600
salallahu alaihi wasallam did not want the message meaning the

00:50:20.600 --> 00:50:26.080
companions to be talking about this so he left in the heat and he started

00:50:26.080 --> 00:50:29.840
to return to Medina Munawwara Usaid ibn Hudayr radiallahu anh who comes

00:50:29.840 --> 00:50:34.040
and he asks he says why are we doing this he says didn't you hear that man

00:50:34.040 --> 00:50:40.160
saying these words Usaid ibn Hudayr says wallahi you are the superior and he is

00:50:40.160 --> 00:50:44.720
the inferior subhanallah so he will be removed not you and this was the

00:50:44.720 --> 00:50:48.680
passion of the Sahabah radiallahu anh may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us

00:50:48.680 --> 00:50:52.720
even a fraction of it for indeed it would elevate us in every single way

00:50:52.720 --> 00:50:58.600
then comes a very very serious story which we will commence this evening

00:50:58.600 --> 00:51:04.360
and inshallah we will continue with tomorrow what had happened is Aisha

00:51:04.360 --> 00:51:07.960
radiallahu anha as they were returning from Banu al-Mustaliq as you heard

00:51:07.960 --> 00:51:11.040
moments ago they were rushing out because of things that had happened

00:51:11.040 --> 00:51:16.720
and at that time they used to be something known as a hodaj on top of

00:51:16.720 --> 00:51:22.280
the camel for the women they were covered in an enclosure a little small

00:51:22.280 --> 00:51:26.320
tent like structure that was on top of the camel which was covering them

00:51:26.320 --> 00:51:30.280
protecting them from the Sun and at the same time being more privacy for them

00:51:30.280 --> 00:51:33.760
and what they used to do when the camel sits they would lift that whole thing

00:51:33.760 --> 00:51:37.840
off and they would put it aside they would go away and the females would

00:51:37.840 --> 00:51:41.160
then engage in whatever they have to and later on when they had to depart

00:51:41.160 --> 00:51:44.360
they would carry it respectfully put it back on the back of the camel and

00:51:44.360 --> 00:51:49.080
they would depart so Aisha radiallahu anha says that when this army was

00:51:49.080 --> 00:51:54.360
there I lost a necklace of mine so I went out to look for this necklace

00:51:54.800 --> 00:51:59.560
and when I was looking for the necklace the army departed they had taken this

00:51:59.560 --> 00:52:03.800
hodaj lifted it thinking I was on as it is I was quite young and I was not

00:52:03.800 --> 00:52:06.960
quite heavy they wouldn't have known if there was a person in there or not

00:52:06.960 --> 00:52:10.480
they put it on the camel and they departed when I got back to where the

00:52:10.480 --> 00:52:16.200
hodaj was I noticed everybody's gone I was shocked and I was dressed in

00:52:16.200 --> 00:52:22.480
black covered in black and she says radiallahu anha I paused for a

00:52:22.480 --> 00:52:26.240
moment they're hoping that they would probably notice that I'm not there and

00:52:26.240 --> 00:52:29.840
they would come back to see me and in the interim I fell asleep when I fell

00:52:29.840 --> 00:52:34.640
asleep Safwani bin Mu'attal radiallahu anhu after some time he was

00:52:34.640 --> 00:52:40.800
passing by and he noticed something black and he stopped and as he stopped

00:52:40.800 --> 00:52:48.520
I got up and when I got up I only heard him say inna lillahi wa inna ilayhi raji'un

00:52:48.560 --> 00:52:53.520
that's all I heard him say nothing else no other statement no greeting no

00:52:53.520 --> 00:52:58.360
talking no nothing there was nothing that happened he only said inna lillahi

00:52:58.360 --> 00:53:03.520
wa inna ilayhi raji'un and he had assisted Aisha radiallahu anha he let

00:53:03.520 --> 00:53:10.680
the camel come down she had got on he let her get onto the camel and took

00:53:10.680 --> 00:53:14.240
her to Madinatul Munawwara when they got to Madinah Munawwara

00:53:14.240 --> 00:53:19.520
Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salool the head of these hypocrites he seized the

00:53:19.520 --> 00:53:27.200
opportunity to create a rumor and what was the rumor the rumor was that Aisha

00:53:27.200 --> 00:53:35.760
has engaged in the sin with Safwani bin Mu'attal and this was the

00:53:35.760 --> 00:53:42.120
purest of the women who existed and she was the wife of the best of

00:53:42.120 --> 00:53:48.480
creation and the man they are making mention of Safwani bin Mu'attal

00:53:48.480 --> 00:53:54.080
was a man who was a very good man as well brilliant never had they heard

00:53:54.080 --> 00:53:58.000
from this Sahabi any form of immorality not at all and so this

00:53:58.000 --> 00:54:02.000
rumor caused a lot of discomfort amongst the people in Madinah

00:54:02.000 --> 00:54:06.280
Munawwara and people began to spread it they were divided into a few

00:54:06.280 --> 00:54:10.120
groups the first group the one who created the rumor his name was

00:54:10.120 --> 00:54:15.320
Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salool the second group those who were responsible

00:54:15.320 --> 00:54:22.760
to spread the rumor and the third group those who did not believe it at

00:54:22.760 --> 00:54:27.720
all and they said this is an absolute fabrication and a lie may Allah

00:54:27.720 --> 00:54:31.120
subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us goodness inshallah tomorrow we will see what

00:54:31.120 --> 00:54:35.160
happened thereafter and how Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala clarified the

00:54:35.160 --> 00:54:38.920
name of Aisha radiallahu anha by revelation that is in Surah al-Nur

00:54:38.960 --> 00:54:43.200
that we read up to this day may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala cleanse us as well

00:54:43.200 --> 00:54:44.720
until we meet again
